  "local_port": 43980,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "I deleted my friend ID from WeChat. How do I find it again?",
  "response": "If you've deleted your friend's ID from WeChat and want to find it again, there are a few methods you can try:\n\n### 1. **Check Your Chat History**\nIf you've had previous conversations with your friend, you might be able to find their ID in your chat history:\n- Open WeChat and go to the \"Chats\" tab.\n- Look for any past conversations with your friend.\n- Their ID should be visible at the top of the chat window.\n\n### 2. **Use WeChat's Search Function**\nYou can use the search function within WeChat to try and find your friend again:\n- Tap on the \"Contacts\" tab.\n- Tap on the search icon (magnifying glass) at the top right corner.\n- Enter any information you remember about your friend (name, phone number, etc.).\n- If their profile comes up, you can see their ID.\n\n### 3. **Check Your Phone Contacts**\nIf your friend's phone number is saved in your phone's contacts and linked to WeChat, you might be able to find them through your phone's address book:\n- Go to the \"Contacts\" tab in WeChat.\n- Tap on \"Add Contacts\" and then \"Find by Mobile Contact.\"\n- Allow WeChat to access your contacts if prompted.\n- If your friend's number is in your contacts and linked to WeChat, their ID should appear.\n\n### 4. **Ask Mutual Friends**\nIf you have mutual friends on WeChat, you can ask them to check your friend's ID:\n- Contact a mutual friend and ask them to look up the ID of the person you're trying to find.\n- They can share the ID with you, and you can then search for it using WeChat's search function.\n\n### 5. **Request the ID Directly**\nIf all else fails, you can try to get in touch with your friend through another means (like email, phone, or another social media platform) and ask them to provide their WeChat ID again.\n\nRemember, if you and your friend are in each other's contact lists, you should be able to find each other again easily using any of these methods.",
